article.description: — Tyler Nelson had 16 points and seven rebounds as Navy narrowly defeated Army 52-49 on Saturday.
article.headline: Nelson scores 16 to lead Navy over Army 52-49
article.linkText: Nelson scores 16 to lead Navy over Army 52-49
article.story: WEST POINT, N.Y. -- — Tyler Nelson had 16 points and seven rebounds as Navy narrowly defeated Army 52-49 on Saturday. Daniel Deaver had 10 points and eight rebounds for Navy (17-8, 10-4 Patriot League). Jalen Rucker had 18 points for the Black Knights (13-13, 7-7), who have now lost four consecutive games. Josh Caldwell added eight rebounds. The Midshipmen leveled the season series against the Black Knights. Army defeated Navy 74-73 on Jan. 22. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
